for better adaptation of an individual with phsychic traumas. So, the research 
of a person`s emotional situation, facing the death, will help to indentify the 
necessity of prophylactic pharmacotherapy with anxiolytics and to overcome both 
the negative associations with death and the fear connected with it (preserving 
