De novo FUS P525L mutation in Juvenile amyotrophic lateral sclerosis with 
dysphonia and diplopia.

Leblond CS(1), Webber A(1), Gan-Or Z(1), Moore F(1), Dagher A(1), Dion PA(1), 
Rouleau GA(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Human Genetics (C.S.L., Z.G.-O.), Montreal Neurological 
