ECONOMIC EVALUATION STUDIES OF SELF-MANAGEMENT INTERVENTIONS IN CHRONIC 
DISEASES: A SYSTEMATIC REVIEW.

van Eeden M(1), van Heugten CM(2), van Mastrigt GA(1), Evers SM(1).
